Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.84,0:00:16.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是如月桃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.10,0:00:20.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.65,0:00:22.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是认错人了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.74,0:00:24.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你们是双胞胎吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.30,0:00:27.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界上还真有长得这么相似的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.31,0:00:34.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的确是如月桃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.64,0:00:36.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 你是我的粉丝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.28,0:00:39.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然非常感谢你喜欢我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.14,0:00:43.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过总是粘着我的话 我会很困扰的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.03,0:00:46.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,签名的话还是可以签的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.51,0:00:47.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.68,0:00:49.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 果然是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.81,0:00:50.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来我就带她回去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.04,0:00:54.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 请好好听人家说话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.07,0:00:57.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 自我介绍有些迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.98,0:00:59.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫木户
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.98,0:00:59.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(455,437)\fs21}Kido
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.58,0:01:01.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是你的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.97,0:01:14.91,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0}act 03 目隐code
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.84,0:03:05.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同伴…你在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.43,0:03:07.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不知道你是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.10,0:03:12.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 是吗 确实太突然了 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.56,0:03:15.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这要怎么说明呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.66,0:03:20.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像被一个奇怪的人缠住了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.53,0:03:23.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总…之先想办法逃走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.36,0:03:24.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 我说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.34,0:03:24.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.38,0:03:26.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就单刀直入地问你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.98,0:03:30.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有没有觉得自己不普通
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.61,0:03:35.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,例如同学 家人 擦肩而过的路人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.17,0:03:38.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和除自己以外的人比较
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.80,0:03:41.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你感受到自己身为「异质」了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.96,0:03:44.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么突然问那种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.59,0:03:45.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我感受到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.48,0:03:50.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去哪儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.33,0:03:53.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是从几岁开始的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.93,0:03:55.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我逐渐从其他人的意识里消失
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.64,0:03:57.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他人的举动仿佛建立在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.88,0:04:04.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从未存在这一事实之上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.11,0:04:07.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那真是令我难以忍受
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.74,0:04:11.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 你和我完全相反
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.96,0:04:15.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算不是你的本意你都会吸引别人目光
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.87,0:04:16.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经意识到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.40,0:04:18.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.22,0:04:22.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是什么人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.70,0:04:25.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都说了 我是你的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.66,0:04:43.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说 无论怎么想都是木户你的错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.32,0:04:45.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只说过为了获取信任
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.56,0:04:48.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微使用一下能力如何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.48,0:04:50.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么…大家在商量的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.90,0:04:53.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是说过稍微威胁一下的话更好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.79,0:04:56.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过那种话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.65,0:04:57.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过吗 茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.76,0:05:00.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我倒是不记得了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.71,0:05:03.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是木户的能力把自己变得像幽灵一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.59,0:05:05.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然展示给对方看 肯定会吓到她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.86,0:05:07.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幽…幽灵？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.85,0:05:11.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来茉莉第一次看到木户能力的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.19,0:05:14.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吓得都跳起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.47,0:05:15.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才没有那种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.91,0:05:18.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不会被吓成那样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.07,0:05:32.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这这这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.30,0:05:33.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.91,0:05:35.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说这里是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.65,0:05:36.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这难道是绑架
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.81,0:05:37.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开玩笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.67,0:05:39.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.58,0:05:40.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是人质！ ？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.89,0:05:44.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧 都怪木户 事情变得麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.51,0:05:45.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.22,0:05:47.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幽灵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.40,0:05:49.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 茉莉 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.90,0:05:57.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎来到我们目隐团基地 新人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.95,0:05:59.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目…隐团？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.20,0:06:00.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.76,0:06:04.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前我们可怕的木户团长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.74,0:06:07.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对你做了失礼的事情 真是非常抱…歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.01,0:06:09.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.52,0:06:13.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之先做自我介绍 我叫鹿野
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.52,0:06:13.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(580,437)\fs21}Kano
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.79,0:06:16.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边摔倒的蓬蓬毛是茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.79,0:06:16.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(562,437)\fs21}Marry
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.82,0:06:18.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家才不是蓬蓬毛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.58,0:06:22.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后那个一心围着茉莉转的大家伙是濑户
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.58,0:06:22.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(668,437)\fs21}Seto
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.70,0:06:24.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那算什么介绍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.45,0:06:27.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 单方面让你受怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.34,0:06:29.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后还带你到这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.30,0:06:30.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.77,0:06:34.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然原本就是想让你过来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.31,0:06:37.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过好像让你产生了误会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.10,0:06:41.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 我看不出你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.63,0:06:42.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 看不出
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.35,0:06:44.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也看到了木户的消失能力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.60,0:06:46.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「目隐」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.99,0:06:49.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看到那个之后就昏过去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.14,0:06:52.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹿野 你很失礼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.32,0:06:55.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.06,0:06:57.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说到哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.13,0:06:59.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了对了 能力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.46,0:07:02.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看到之后有什么想法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.86,0:07:03.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么想…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.14,0:07:06.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说那真的是消失了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.90,0:07:09.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 那也不可能是超能力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.38,0:07:10.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法相信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.01,0:07:13.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也觉得不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.45,0:07:15.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为…什么要那么做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.27,0:07:18.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看了这个之后还想向你搭话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.85,0:07:21.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的报导？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.28,0:07:23.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看了这个之后…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.14,0:07:25.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又不是星探什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.92,0:07:32.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…难道在演唱会中途换了彩色隐形眼镜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.26,0:07:34.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有换吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.07,0:07:39.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你会知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.19,0:07:42.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木户也说过了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.18,0:07:45.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是你的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.31,0:07:52.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.41,0:07:57.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说你一直以来都保密眼睛的能力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.68,0:07:59.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从小时候就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.70,0:08:03.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我记不清具体是什么时候开始的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.71,0:08:05.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从某个时期开始
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.32,0:08:07.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.72,0:08:09.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做的事情都变得异常受人瞩目
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.24,0:08:12.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「目夺」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.25,0:08:14.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你才成为偶像的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.23,0:08:18.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是和木户完全不同的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.99,0:08:22.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开开…都说了是开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.61,0:08:25.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木户的能力很厉害也十分可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.26,0:08:26.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛痛痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.98,0:08:30.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 我什么都不说了 真的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.45,0:08:32.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉那么吵闹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.84,0:08:35.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.43,0:08:37.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来 我真吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.57,0:08:41.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到除了我还有人拥有这种能力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.93,0:08:44.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们小时候和如月你一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.10,0:08:47.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家眼睛都变红了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.59,0:08:50.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最初真的有很多麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.45,0:08:53.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过幸亏我们能像这样在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.08,0:08:57.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相互帮助 才总算捡回了一条命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.80,0:09:01.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗 你们关系不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.32,0:09:02.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只是一段孽缘而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.30,0:09:05.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情就是这样 如月
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.60,0:09:06.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.58,0:09:12.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的能力和我们的能力是一样的没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.03,0:09:15.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 根据我们的观察来看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.52,0:09:17.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还没有熟练使用那种能力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.28,0:09:21.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正如你所说 今天我也狼狈不堪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.80,0:09:24.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事 没有习惯的话就会那样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.65,0:09:26.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过去木户也这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.13,0:09:30.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这样下去的话就会消失掉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.05,0:09:40.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此我们想帮你让你能够掌握你的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.43,0:09:43.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少能让你学会控制能力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.83,0:09:45.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以避免再次发生像今天那样的骚动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.33,0:09:47.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以做到那种事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.34,0:09:51.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是做不到 我现在就是空气了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.93,0:09:53.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.08,0:09:55.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底什么时候能学乖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.80,0:09:57.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.80,0:10:01.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是说 如果我能控制好能力的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.16,0:10:05.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就能像普通的女孩子一样出门购物了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.25,0:10:08.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以和朋友聊天吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.50,0:10:10.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部都得看你自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.48,0:10:15.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少我非常希望你能成为团员
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.58,0:10:16.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至于最后的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.96,0:10:19.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算那不是你的本意也会实现吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.72,0:10:23.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明交到朋友很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.95,0:10:25.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还真不坦率啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.58,0:10:27.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了算了 不是挺好的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.62,0:10:29.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变得热闹起来 真是不错的一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.40,0:10:31.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我泡了茶哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.24,0:10:33.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要加入
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.68,0:10:34.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目目团
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.39,0:10:53.03,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,再见 再见 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.50,0:10:54.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.06,0:10:57.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起对不起对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.60,0:11:00.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手机…也许不能用了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.43,0:11:04.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉 在什么都没有的地方都能摔倒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.63,0:11:05.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.22,0:11:09.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.50,0:11:18.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个笨蛋 会妨碍到我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.63,0:11:20.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 这到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.82,0:11:23.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是茉莉的「目夺」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.42,0:11:28.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与她对视之人几分钟之内会完全失去行动能力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.69,0:11:34.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…应该不会有生命危险吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.69,0:11:42.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.81,0:11:45.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 好像都是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.01,0:11:49.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说都是茉莉弄坏了你的手机
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.81,0:11:50.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.05,0:11:52.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.74,0:11:56.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外 我的能力可以抵消你的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.07,0:11:59.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也算是得到了不错的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.72,0:12:02.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏你我有一种变成了透明人的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.13,0:12:05.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,团长的能力真是厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.26,0:12:07.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然可以让什么东西都能消失
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.60,0:12:15.22,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,完全…不会…被人发现
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.80,0:12:13.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过一旦被人碰到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.45,0:12:14.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,效果就会立刻解除
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.12,0:12:20.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实这是将一定距离之内的物体
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.12,0:12:22.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对自己的认知无限稀薄的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.84,0:12:26.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来它很适合用在小如月身上 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.10,0:12:30.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来 这件事有必要大家全都来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.33,0:12:34.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小茉莉 不要哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.32,0:12:38.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹿野 虽然换手机是我自己的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.83,0:12:42.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是大家要一起来重新买打碎的玻璃杯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.59,0:12:44.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是事先已经取得大家同意了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.37,0:12:45.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是开玩笑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.00,0:12:47.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别生气嘛 小如月
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.31,0:12:49.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是濑户的提案哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.10,0:12:51.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是挺好的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.67,0:12:55.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得出来买东西还是大家一起比较开心嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.31,0:12:58.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK OK 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.90,0:13:01.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么总之先去换手机吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.15,0:13:04.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 我去找店子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.72,0:13:10.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.94,0:13:12.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.76,0:13:15.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你哥哥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.70,0:13:17.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的啊 长得有点像
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.89,0:13:22.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实有一点神似呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.57,0:13:24.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不愧是兄妹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.42,0:13:28.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人是你哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.34,0:13:33.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 不用你管啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.35,0:13:36.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 鹿野你笑得太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.25,0:13:37.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.56,0:13:39.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来为什么他会在这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.24,0:13:41.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平常明明从来不出门的 偏偏今天…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.25,0:13:43.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.18,0:13:45.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太糟糕了太糟糕了太糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.65,0:13:49.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 如月 刚刚那个人是你的哥哥吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.49,0:13:51.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说呢…那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.61,0:13:53.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真是神似呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.56,0:13:57.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很啰嗦 请不要管这些
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.61,0:13:59.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.65,0:14:02.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 赶紧办完正事回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.44,0:14:03.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽可能快的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.85,0:14:11.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来情况有些不妙呢 木户
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.11,0:14:12.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.04,0:14:14.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 我们得从楼梯下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.36,0:14:16.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.22,0:14:22.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你哥哥那边让我去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.32,0:14:24.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之你先待在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.22,0:14:31.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 鹿野
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.22,0:14:34.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,濑户 你也跟着去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.47,0:14:36.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在这里 她们没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.82,0:14:37.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.13,0:14:40.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉 你要好好跟着木户哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.00,0:14:42.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要走了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.02,0:14:46.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉 别哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.17,0:14:46.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.90,0:14:49.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,濑户 紧急情况
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.80,0:14:51.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天你也使用能力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.45,0:14:56.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我不太情愿 了解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.70,0:15:02.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.34,0:15:10.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹿野他到底怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.25,0:15:13.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会不会被抓到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.83,0:15:15.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人面对那么多人 不可能的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.14,0:15:17.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被抓住了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.30,0:15:19.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正常情况下肯定被抓了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.43,0:15:23.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是他有那种能力 应该不会被抓到的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.48,0:15:27.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.48,0:15:28.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.91,0:15:29.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是笨蛋发过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.07,0:15:35.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.61,0:15:39.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说面对这种情况为什么这个人还这么游刃有余
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.30,0:15:41.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是鹿野啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.57,0:15:42.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看上去好像很开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.55,0:15:44.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙的能力是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.99,0:15:47.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能让别人眼中的自己变成另外一副模样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.01,0:15:50.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简单来说 就是「目欺」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.16,0:15:52.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许他拍这张照片的时候也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.29,0:15:57.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在袭击犯那些家伙看来他是被绑起来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.03,0:16:01.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是这样 这家伙还真是个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.94,0:16:03.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直无可救药
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.62,0:16:05.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs21}Mail 鹿野
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.62,0:16:05.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs21}我是鹿野~。我在小如月的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.62,0:16:05.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs21}哥哥身边，身为人质中！濑户
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.62,0:16:05.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs21}对我说你们非常担心、所以就
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.62,0:16:05.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs21}发了照片给你们要打起精神来哦~。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.78,0:16:07.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs21}Mail 鹿野
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.78,0:16:07.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs21}我说木户你啊总是说人家是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.78,0:16:07.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs21}笨蛋什么的不是很过分吗？尽管
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.78,0:16:07.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs21}如此人家还是很危险的啊。稍微
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.78,0:16:07.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs21}担心一下我也不错的说~总之为了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.78,0:16:07.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs21}不让你一个人寂寞先拍了张照片
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.78,0:16:07.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs21}发给你了哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.05,0:16:08.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs21}是否删除？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.60,0:16:09.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs21}已删除。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.96,0:16:14.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么鹿野他听得到我们说话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.42,0:16:16.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是他的能力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.02,0:16:21.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是濑户因为他拥有窃取别人思想的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.02,0:16:25.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过他本人非常讨厌 很少使用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.65,0:16:28.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样看来大家真的很像是超能力者呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.02,0:16:33.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 貌似至少我们的对话能传达过去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.20,0:16:35.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.98,0:16:37.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能想办法打倒他们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.88,0:16:39.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靠各位的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.53,0:16:41.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你指的是击退他们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.91,0:16:43.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是不要抱太大的希望比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.82,0:16:48.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们之中还没有能与持枪的人为敌的武斗派哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.98,0:16:49.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.45,0:16:52.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然如此 即使要逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.41,0:16:55.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要这个建筑的电气系统还在敌人的把握之中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.04,0:16:57.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卷帘门也打不开呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.02,0:17:02.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去也无法带着你的哥哥逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.07,0:17:05.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,况且我哥哥已经被抓住了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.78,0:17:08.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.27,0:17:10.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.09,0:17:14.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我大概想到了一个好办法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.50,0:17:23.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确认耳机里传来了女生的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.36,0:17:25.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来和你说的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.99,0:17:29.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然小贵音也一起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.06,0:17:32.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个叫贵音的是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.90,0:17:36.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想想…电视里说的那种超级厉害的黑客之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.14,0:17:37.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种感觉的女孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.83,0:17:42.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是看上去 哥哥好像有什么打算
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.34,0:17:43.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹿野那里还发来了其他的内容哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.39,0:17:46.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要让你的哥哥瞄准机会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.53,0:17:49.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能执行一个成功率100%的秘策
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.17,0:17:51.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.04,0:17:52.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.08,0:17:54.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 小茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.72,0:17:56.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你手上拿的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.85,0:18:00.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,武器 我也想努力…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.74,0:18:18.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你小子当你揍的是谁的脑袋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.60,0:18:22.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你倒是说些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.33,0:18:25.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什么呢 想死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.07,0:18:26.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.69,0:18:28.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉心跳都要停了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.38,0:18:31.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之从这里开始要慎重一点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.79,0:18:33.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这关系到人命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.64,0:18:34.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.67,0:18:37.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你小子唧唧歪歪说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.70,0:18:40.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如月 怎么样 可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.42,0:18:42.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,插入曲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.10,0:18:57.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说白了只要把卷帘门打开就行了对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.27,0:19:02.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概靠我哥哥和另外一个女孩子应该做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.15,0:19:05.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然这要和鹿野确定一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.11,0:19:09.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那当然可以
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.19,0:19:11.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是要怎么制造让你哥哥逃出去的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.51,0:19:14.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我多多少少可以感觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.83,0:19:17.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁在什么地方做什么事情可以吸引别人的注意力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.22,0:19:20.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以那个机会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.49,0:19:21.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就由我来创造
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.57,0:19:31.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看见了 就是那里的电视
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.97,0:19:36.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才应该一辈子待在监狱里吧 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.31,0:19:42.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还在装什么帅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.48,0:20:02.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,团长 小茉莉 就是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.35,0:20:33.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如月桃 16岁 是一位偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.06,0:20:39.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.12,0:20:47.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.93,0:22:24.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类开始畏惧 厌恶怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.10,0:22:28.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有的人扔石头 有的人会放火
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.00,0:22:32.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们用各种各样的方法袭击她想要杀死怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.42,0:22:36.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「为什么我一定要遭受这种事情」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.50,0:22:40.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每当怪物被人类伤害的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.37,0:22:41.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被刺痛的内心深处都会发出阵阵悲鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.90,0:22:49.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从此诞生的恐惧在心中深深扎根变换形态
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.63,0:22:51.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知从何时开始
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.09,0:22:55.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪物的心中已经堆满了各种对人类的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.10,0:22:58.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一种又一种的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.04,0:23:01.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仿佛是在保护怪物一样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.61,0:23:05.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从内心溢出 改变怪物的外表
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.41,0:23:12.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感情得以表现的怪物得到了强大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.95,0:23:14.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀掉了很多的人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.24,0:23:22.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次杀死人的那一天 怪物哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.10,0:23:25.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二天也是 第三天也是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.15,0:23:29.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像幼小的少女一样 不断地哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.90,0:23:54.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,111)\bord0\fs27\shad2}act04:阳炎days
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.90,0:23:42.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天能好好说出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.74,0:23:45.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须趁我还在这里的时候告诉她才行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.09,0:23:48.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我并不讨厌夏天哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.43,0:23:51.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 我消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OP
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.21,0:01:34.10,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}コンクリートが揺らいだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.16,0:01:36.61,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}霞み燻む、君の望ている夢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.08,0:01:38.75,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}テンプレートをなぞった
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.83,0:01:40.72,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}知らないままの日常
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.87,0:01:43.61,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}ハイテンポなアテンダンス
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.69,0:01:46.26,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}消えない　足りない　落ち込んだ未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.69,0:01:48.49,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}最終話が来たって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.58,0:01:50.75,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}言えない　君は泣きそう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.95,0:01:52.32,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}ほら、目を閉じて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.41,0:01:53.77,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}迷子なら一緒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.86,0:01:55.75,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}帰り道もないでしょう？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.83,0:01:58.99,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}継ぎ接いでた　秘密に願う
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.07,0:02:00.42,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}未来は平凡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.62,0:02:02.02,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}さぁ、手を鳴らせ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.10,0:02:06.41,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}０で廻った　勘違いを今日も集めて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.50,0:02:07.53,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}始めよう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.61,0:02:10.35,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}君もまた、無我夢中？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.42,0:02:11.12,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}Let's 「play」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.20,0:02:12.78,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}届くまで叫んで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.85,0:02:13.57,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}Let's 「save」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.65,0:02:15.23,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}叶うまで足掻いて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.30,0:02:17.62,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}その手を掴むまで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.69,0:02:20.18,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}この温度は忘れない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.26,0:02:20.82,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}Let's 「daze」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.88,0:02:22.46,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}心を消さないで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.53,0:02:23.24,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}Let's 「change」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.32,0:02:25.04,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}一人で泣かないで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.12,0:02:27.24,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}「孤独」なら　塗り替えれる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.31,0:02:32.81,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}「ひとりぼっち」を変えようとした君となら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.21,0:01:34.10,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}混凝土震颤着的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.16,0:01:36.61,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}笼罩在霞光中的 你一直看着的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.08,0:01:38.75,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}点缀着范式的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.83,0:01:40.72,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}依然一无所知的日常
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.87,0:01:43.61,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}快速参与其中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.69,0:01:46.26,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}不会消失 无法满足 消沉的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.69,0:01:48.49,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}最终话就要到来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.58,0:01:50.75,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}说不出这句话的你泫然欲泣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.95,0:01:52.32,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}来 闭上眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.41,0:01:53.77,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}我们迷途之人应当一起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.86,0:01:55.75,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}你也没有归宿之处对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.83,0:01:58.99,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}不断接续着 悄悄地许愿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.07,0:02:00.42,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}未来是平凡的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.62,0:02:02.02,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}来 击掌为证
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.10,0:02:06.41,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}今天也从零开始聚集一切误解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.50,0:02:07.53,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.61,0:02:10.35,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}你是否也迷途梦中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.42,0:02:11.12,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}Let's 「play」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.20,0:02:12.78,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}吼叫到传达给你为止
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.85,0:02:13.57,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}Let's 「save」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.65,0:02:15.23,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}挣扎到实现为止
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.30,0:02:17.62,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}直到紧握住那只手为止
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.69,0:02:20.18,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}我不会忘记这份温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.26,0:02:20.82,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}Let's 「daze」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.88,0:02:22.46,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}不要消却真心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.53,0:02:23.24,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}Let's 「change」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.32,0:02:25.04,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}不要独自哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.12,0:02:27.24,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}「孤独」什么的 是可以重写的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.31,0:02:32.81,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}与想要不再「一人独处」的你在一起的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.00,0:20:57.05,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}意味のないままで　期間は過ぎて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.86,0:21:06.86,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}理解しようとして　気づいた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.90,0:21:14.89,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}遠く離れた笑え声なんも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.14,0:21:21.83,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}どこにも聞こえない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.85,0:21:27.20,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}涙が落ちる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.54,0:21:32.71,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}これが未来だというならいっそう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.79,0:21:37.53,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}やりきってない明日を手放して
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.96,0:21:43.38,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}声の聞こえない場所に
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.61,0:21:47.41,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}一人でいよう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.61,0:21:52.50,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}暮れる世界の涙を知って
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.69,0:21:58.20,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}溢れ出す理不尽を数えても
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.29,0:22:14.58,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}こんな日々を　おくる意味はきっと見つけられないなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.00,0:20:57.05,EDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}毫无意义的日子里 期限却已过
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.86,0:21:06.86,EDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}想要去理解 却察觉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.90,0:21:14.89,EDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}分隔在遥远之地的笑声
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.14,0:21:21.83,EDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}在哪里也听不到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.85,0:21:27.20,EDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}眼泪都落下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.54,0:21:32.71,EDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}如果这就是未来的话 还不服
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.79,0:21:37.53,EDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}果敢地放弃还没有到来的明天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.96,0:21:43.38,EDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}在听不见声音的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.61,0:21:47.41,EDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}一个人静一会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.61,0:21:52.50,EDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}就算知道逝去世界的眼泪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.69,0:21:58.20,EDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}就算列举溢出的荒谬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.29,0:22:14.58,EDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}这样度过每一天的意义 最后也一定不会找到
